{"word":"ὑποκάμπτω","slug":"ὑποκάμπτω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὑποκάμπτω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>ψω</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to bend short back, turn in under</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> <i>to turn short back, double</i> as a hare, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:—<a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a>, <i>to fall short of</i>, <el>καιρόν</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}